description:
Do you ever feel emotionally trapped, controlled by feelings that overwhelm you? How do you get out of such traps? What is the key to overcoming challenges that threaten your sense of well-being? In this presentation Dan Gabbert reinforces the importance of examining our thoughts so we can correct them and replace them with God’s thoughts about challenges that come our way. Learn how thought patterns can produce automatic negative responses, leading us to fall into emotional traps. Find out how to handle challenging situations that threaten your self-worth. Discover the truth that will free you from emotional traps.
